# Financial Risk Capital Adequacy Margin Options Percent

## identifier
de5480

## type
float

## definition
Report the Capital Adequacy Margin applied to the best estimate assumptions of options, as per the capital adequacy standard. The margin must be applied so as to produce a more conservative estimate of the liability than best estimate.

## syntax
### xbrl
- name=FinancialRisk.CapitalAdequacy.MarginOptions.Percent
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.05
- period=instant
